@node 概説, 特徴, Top, Top
@chapter 『かんな／ｅｍａｃｓ』とは？
@c %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
@c @dm @multiply@jintercharskip by 30@multiply@jasciikanjiskip by 30
@cindex かんな[かんな]
@cindex Nemacs
@cindex Mule
@cindex cannaserver
